-- U.S. RESEARCH ROUNDUP-Foot Locker, InterMune, Monsanto
-- 
-- Mon Aug 25, 2014 02:34AM EDT
-- None



Aug 25 (Reuters) - Wall Street securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several U.S.-listed companies, including Avalanche Biotechnologies, Foot Locker and InterMune, on Monday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Avalanche Biotechnologies <AAVL.O>: Jefferies starts with buy rating; $40 target price * Foot Locker Inc <FL.N>: Barclays, Canaccord Genuity raise target price on the stock * InterMune Inc <ITMN.O>: Leerink, Baird raise target price on the stock   Following is a summary of research actions on U.S. companies reported by Reuters on Monday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order. * Aeropostale Inc <ARO.N>: Susquehanna cuts target price to $6 from $8; rating positive * Amphenol Corp <APH.N>: RBC raises target price to $107 from $101; rating top pick * Avalanche Biotechnologies <AAVL.O>: Jefferies starts with buy rating; $40 target price * Bio Blast Pharma Ltd <ORPN.O>: Roth Capital starts with buy rating; target price of $15 * Chimerix Inc <CMRX.O>: Morgan Stanley cuts target price to $33 from $34; rating overweight * Duke Energy Corp <DUK.N>: RBC raises target price to $81 from $80; rating outperform * Foot Locker Inc <FL.N>: Canaccord Genuity raises target price to $59 from $56; rating buy * Foot Locker Inc <FL.N>: Barclays raises target price to $60 from $50; rating equal weight * InterMune Inc <ITMN.O>: Baird raises target price to $74 from $50; rating outperform * InterMune Inc <ITMN.O>: Leerink raises target price to $74 from $53; rating outperform * Macrocure Ltd <MCUR.O>: Jefferies starts with buy rating; $14 target price * Monsanto Co <MON.N>: Jefferies cuts target price to $130 from $140; rating hold * Splunk <SPLK.O>: Cowen and Company adjusts target price to $55; rating outperform * State Auto Financial <STFC.O>: KBW raises target to $23.50 from $22.50; market perform * XG Technology INC <XGTI.O>: Roth Capital starts with buy rating; $5 target price